rows.label: bf04370130_0015
rows.name:
Profusest apologies for letting
them control Kiku like that...

rows.label: bf04370130_0020
rows.name:
(Kiku show much more respect
for Masterpon than Hana do...)

rows.label: bf04370130_0030
rows.name:
No need for apologies. You come
back, and that enough for me.

rows.label: bf04370130_0050
rows.name: Hana used to people doing awful things.

rows.label: bf04370130_0070
rows.name: Hana, Kiku has one more request.

rows.label: bf04370130_0080
rows.name:
Hana will save them.
It is my duty.

rows.label: bf04370130_0095
rows.name: Now Kiku has one thing left to do...

rows.label: bf04370130_0125
rows.name:
Using experimental ether furnace from Kiku,
it can be fully ignited!

rows.label: bf04370130_0140
rows.name: Will Kiku be all right doing thing like that?!

rows.label: bf04370130_0155
rows.name: Use the flames of Kiku's life...to save them...
